{"tid":1782471,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做實事,求教學,到底如何註冊社團?請高手指點","createTime":"2019-12-14T03:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T19:07:29.000Z","uid":269287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d9974c7bfa8aeb63d3fcfddfda61d7b8c45a8d7f","tid":1782471,"uid":269287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T03:40:44.000Z","msg":"各位, 為左可以投票選特首選委, 我希望可以申請一個社團, 不過攞左張表格, 填表時有疑問, 希望有高質連登仔可以比個教學我<br />\n疑問:<br />\n<br />\n1) 申請豁免註冊社團是否一樣可以係特首選委同功能組別投票?<br />\n2) 社團宗旨點寫先會規格? 是否一定要提供社團規章, 組織章程同會議記錄? 有沒有範本?<br />\n3) 業務地點可唔可以寫自己屋企個住址?<br />\n4) 是否一定要整個社團原子印章?<br />\n<br />\n求解答"},{"pid":"fef4e61db04d699f2f0de6d6ff7bc297debc809a","tid":1782471,"uid":106094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9974c7bfa8aeb63d3fcfddfda61d7b8c45a8d7f","tid":1782471,"uid":269287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T03:40:44.000Z","msg":"各位, 為左可以投票選特首選委, 我希望可以申請一個社團, 不過攞左張表格, 填表時有疑問, 希望有高質連登仔可以比個教學我<br />\n疑問:<br />\n<br />\n1) 申請豁免註冊社團是否一樣可以係特首選委同功能組別投票?<br />\n2) 社團宗旨點寫先會規格? 是否一定要提供社團規章, 組織章程同會議記錄? 有沒有範本?<br />\n3) 業務地點可唔可以寫自己屋企個住址?<br />\n4) 是否一定要整個社團原子印章?<br />\n<br />\n求解答"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T19:07:29.000Z","msg":"1. 是<br />\n<br />\n2. 社團宗旨可以係：推廣________<br />\n社團規章、組織章程或會議記錄：三揀一都得<br />\n顯示到社團宗旨或目的就得<br />\n範本請入 TG 谷<br />\n▸ <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Cd9xTVNjRXjQUQuoWiSPDw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FCd9xTVNjRXjQUQuoWiSPDw&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIO2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=30b15872\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Cd9xTVNjRXjQUQuoWiSPDw</a><br />\n再跳去呢個 Message<br />\n▸ <a href=\"http://t.me/c/1399014776/5674\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fc%2F1399014776%2F5674&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIO2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=1fb2f088\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/c/1399014776/5674</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 可以，地址會出街嘅地方：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/11_useful_info/licences/list_of_societies.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F11_useful_info%2Flicences%2Flist_of_societies.html&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIO2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=57d1454b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/11_useful_info/licences/list_of_societies.html</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 否"}]}